description:
Sakurai Yukino a high school junior and http://anidb.net/ch11337 [Kanade]`s elder twin. She likes snacks and often trades photos of Kanade to their friend http://anidb.net/ch11339 [Sakuya] for them. She is a member of their school`s swim team and writes a daily blog about her life. She cares deeply for Kanade and will support her in any way she can.
